text: Ðis syndan ðæs dennes land gemæru to Hæselersce.
Ærest andlang Fearnleges burnan oð runanleages mearce, of runanleages mearce be holanbeames mearce, of holanbeames mearce swa on gerihte to wiglege bufan ðære smiþðan to þam geate.
Of þam geate innan þæne sihter, andlang sihtres innan þære bradan burnan, niðer andland bradan burnan, be þæs arcebisceopes mearce eft innan fearnleages burnan.
Ðis is þæs dennes boc æt Hæselersce þe Cnut cing gebocode ælfstane arcebisceope on ece yrfe.
